txt.en: Speak to the commander to begin the assault.
Speak to the Commander to begin the assault
Dol Amroth has been taken by corsairs. Select the area of the city you wish to retake then speak to the commander to begin.
'You know your orders. Let us retake Dol Amroth! To battle!'
Before the operation can begin, you must select which area of the city you wish to retake.
Speak to the soldiers and select your target building
